{"tid":2215960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地上一攤血！驚傳男大生學校廁所自宮　只因「怕性欲影響學習」","createTime":"2020-09-24T10:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T11:35:55.000Z","uid":149959,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"99a0d43944d78562625f1558ca53097ab2d29cb8","tid":2215960,"uid":149959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"根據了解，該男學生因為有考研究所的規劃，覺得自己必須更認真讀書，不能被性欲左右，他認為欲望會干擾自己的讀書狀態，所以決定自行下手「解決」分心源頭，到廁所親手「閹割」小鳥，被發現後緊急送醫治療，極端行徑也快速在校內傳開。<br />\n<br />\n據傳校方已將男大生進行閹割的廁所封閉，但男大生為了認真讀書不惜自殘的行為已引起熱議。有人認為該學生可能有精神方面的疾病、或者被極端論壇洗腦，也有人表示當局應該更加重視性教育相關議題，避免憾事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20200924web004/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20200924web004%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=7f2cddf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20200924web004/</a>"},{"pid":"dbbd0471a90fa4a41790245d16d84dbd12e2b9ea","tid":2215960,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"蕭 別離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f902e867547ba51502c35e1ca0cc1f9d3c7e7c","tid":2215960,"uid":343268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"828ae6ce416ad47a1845ccb0dd4329f47853e91f","tid":2215960,"uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbbd0471a90fa4a41790245d16d84dbd12e2b9ea","tid":2215960,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"蕭 別離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"佢最近破左戒，所以要自宮俾返D說服力俾班教徒睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198ad8cd775f20ed2a36484d5f38b804c6944341","tid":2215960,"uid":149959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbbd0471a90fa4a41790245d16d84dbd12e2b9ea",